{"tid":1059842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（世紀難題）影相vs照鏡","createTime":"2019-03-13T11:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:50:34.000Z","uid":69621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d40f396a42e17d77081d79372ec1d34bd70738e2","tid":1059842,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"一個困擾咗我好耐嘅難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟影相同照鏡邊個先係真嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網search 過有人話影相係真，因為照鏡下意識會縮細自己缺點<br />\n又有人話照鏡先係真，因為相係平面<br />\n我自己成日覺得照鏡正正常常，但影相出到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇高人解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aec938d7e26bfc7807854358d82953e822051fa","tid":1059842,"uid":129712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"影相先係真，<br />\n因為鏡係左右反轉"},{"pid":"47b551201ffd510bb38a5fcafdade8cdf1a11bfd","tid":1059842,"uid":227166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"問吓身邊嘅人 究竟係影相似你平時多啲 定係鏡入面嘅你似平時多啲<br />\n利申：我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb94385fda0949500ab0d20affd8e3a8bb4fa22","tid":1059842,"uid":69621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0aec938d7e26bfc7807854358d82953e822051fa","tid":1059842,"uid":129712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"影相先係真，<br />\n因為鏡係左右反轉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"但自拍嗰陣唔係都左右反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962eb4a5bac0d392a50c27e91a3f7e1204e8733f","tid":1059842,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47b551201ffd510bb38a5fcafdade8cdf1a11bfd","tid":1059842,"uid":227166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"問吓身邊嘅人 究竟係影相似你平時多啲 定係鏡入面嘅你似平時多啲<br />\n利申：我都想知<img 